songs.title: Intro (I Love You)
songs.album: I Love You (A Dedication To My Fans)
songs.lyrics:
[Spoken: Jadakiss]
Here we go again
You know what it is
Real recognize real
We've seen a lot of MCs come and go in this game
But me? Ha!
I'm still here
And I owe it all to you
My fans
So to show my gratitude and appreciation
I just wanted to let you know...
